# Input

```html
@let    name   =      'Frodo';
<h1>Dashboard for {{name}}</h1>
Hello, {{name}}

```


# Prettier differences

```diff
--- Prettier
+++ Biome
@@ -1,3 +1,3 @@
-@let name = "Frodo";
-<h1>Dashboard for {{ name }}</h1>
-Hello, {{ name }}
+@let name = 'Frodo';
+<h1>Dashboard for {{name}}</h1>
+Hello, {{name}}
```

# Output

```html
@let name = 'Frodo';
<h1>Dashboard for {{name}}</h1>
Hello, {{name}}
```

